sentences.english: Lampetra japonica could migrate to the Yellow Sea region and freshwater in Jiangsu Province.
sentences.chinese: 日本七鰓鰻可以遷移到黃海及江蘇省淡水中。

sentences.english: Sea lampreys leave a swath of destruction as the invasive species chomps through the Great Lakes.
sentences.chinese: 七鰓鰻留下一條致命的傷口，其在五大湖大行其道。

sentences.english: Japanese Lamprey is one of the most primitive extant vertebrate.
sentences.chinese: 日本七鰓鰻是現存最原始而特化的脊椎動物之一。

sentences.english: Any of several similar fishes, such as the lamprey and electric eel.
sentences.chinese: 與八目鰻類魚區別開的七鰓鰻。
